	<h1 class="title">油价下跌了， 但为什么你花了更多的钱在油上？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/130051/small/130051.jpg?1435571000" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">温欣语 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-27 06:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/16612/medium/16612.jpg?1445852615" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="16612" data-title="《油价下跌了， 但为什么你花了更多的钱在油上？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/16612/medium/16612.jpg?1445852615" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/16612.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
